Reasoning: The paper discusses the design and simulation of microrobots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of simulation tools for predicting the motion and performance of microrobots suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of mechanical engineering (cs.ME). The study of microrobots and their motion also involves the use of electronics and control systems, which could place the paper in the sub-category of embedded systems (cs.ET) or systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper may also belong to the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM) as it discusses the use of simulation tools for visualizing the motion of microrobots.
